$Id

Preliminary README file for M.

To install:
  ./configure --help
  ./configure "with your appropriate options"
  make depend
  make
  make doc
  make install_all

  to rebuild M source, run make from the src sub directory

Documentation can be found in the doc directory:

doc/README - what this should be
doc/OSF    - notes about M on DEC OSF/1
doc/Manual - what will become the manual

